{
  "stem": "17330.1",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 304.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I went to the people I was supposed to go to and I said, I'm going to give myself up and I'm not staying here and I [INAUDIBLE] myself in.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 81,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they said no, you've got a baby and you're not.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 82,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Anyway, half an hour later, the military police came.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 83,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Sittard.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "The-- the-- the customer was-- I can't remember what the name was.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Very nice people.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I've got a photo in the kitchen from it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Anyway, [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the military police took me away and brought me to the military place where they stayed.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And I didn't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And in the night, I don't know how many times I called them, then I had an excuse, a bit of water, then I had to go to the toilet, any excuse to talk.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But there was no talking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 84,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then the next morning, they took us to another town, Maastricht.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The military police and my husband, because they put him in another cell.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] then we came in in Maastricht, and there was the jail.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he was put in the men's section and I was put in the woman's.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And I stayed there for 12 days with two other people in a cell what was original for one woman, for one person.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 85,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Dutch borders, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 86,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then after 12 days--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They gave you food.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 87,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But you have to-- to live in a little space what actually was for one person.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That was one lady who was caught at the border.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She wanted to go over the border.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 88,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the other one was not Jewish at all, but married to a Jew.",
      "word_count": 14
    }
  ],
